        "title": "feat(browser): surface observed dialogs",
        "body": "## Summary\n- track managed-browser modal dialogs as pending/recent browser state and expose that state through action, snapshot, and debug responses\n- let browser dialog actions answer a still-pending dialog by id while preserving arm-next-dialog behavior\n- guard dialog state with current-URL policy, reject unsupported existing-session dialog ids, and document the CLI/docs behavior\n\n## Verification\n- `node scripts/run-vitest.mjs extensions/browser/src/browser-tool.test.ts extensions/browser/src/browser/pw-session.dialogs.test.ts extensions/browser/src/browser/pw-tools-core.interactions.evaluate.abort.test.ts extensions/browser/src/browser/server.agent-contract-core.test.ts extensions/browser/src/browser/server.agent-contract-form-layout-act-commands.test.ts extensions/browser/src/browser/routes/agent.existing-session.test.ts`\n- `node scripts/run-vitest.mjs extensions/browser/src/browser/client.test.ts extensions/browser/src/browser-tool.test.ts extensions/browser/src/browser/pw-session.dialogs.test.ts extensions/browser/src/browser/server.agent-contract-core.test.ts`\n- `git diff --check`\n- `env CI=1 NODE_OPTIONS=--max-old-space-size=4096 OPENCLAW_TEST_PROJECTS_PARALLEL=6 OPENCLAW_VITEST_MAX_WORKERS=1 OPENCLAW_VITEST_NO_OUTPUT_TIMEOUT_MS=900000 pnpm check:changed`\n- `/Users/steipete/Projects/agent-scripts/skills/codex-review/scripts/codex-review`\n\nBehavior addressed: Managed browser actions and snapshots now expose pending modal dialog state, and dialog actions can target a still-pending dialog id.\nReal environment tested: local browser test harness and local changed gate in this checkout\nExact steps or command run after this patch: see Verification\nEvidence after fix: focused dialog/control-server/browser-tool tests passed; `pnpm check:changed` passed for extensions, extensionTests, and docs lanes; Codex review reported no actionable findings\nObserved result after fix: action-triggered dialogs return `blockedByDialog` with pending id